The paper discusses machine learning methods such as neural networks and decision trees, which are commonly used in the field of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also focuses on multi-class classification, which falls under the category of data mining (cs.DM). The use of oblique decision surfaces and random vector functional link network suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper proposes an ensemble classifier, which is a common topic in the field of machine learning (cs.LG).
